2
00:00:11,413 --> 00:00:14,272
=The Glory Fades=

3
00:00:14,272 --> 00:00:16,992
=Episode 6=
(Death Temperature)

4
00:00:18,912 --> 00:00:19,853
(Twenty Minutes Ago)

5
00:00:19,853 --> 00:00:20,693
