12
00:00:43,956 --> 00:00:44,916
It's complicated.

13
00:00:45,120 --> 00:00:46,397
Listen, Bai Manni.

14
00:00:47,136 --> 00:00:49,596
Don't always rely on

15
00:00:49,596 --> 00:00:51,876
Tu Jiasheng and Lu to cover for you.

16
00:00:52,636 --> 00:00:53,757
My presence here

17
00:00:54,077 --> 00:00:55,200
is honoring you.

18
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,437
I'm making you money!

19
00:00:59,516 --> 00:01:02,037
Either move me to the Tian Level,

20
00:01:02,157 --> 00:01:03,117
or

21
00:01:03,236 --> 00:01:04,757
have a drink with me.

22
00:01:04,832 --> 00:01:06,240
Or let this little girl

23
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:07,836
