24
00:01:08,757 --> 00:01:09,516
Lu.

25
00:01:09,516 --> 00:01:10,676
You have three choices.

26
00:01:11,168 --> 00:01:12,357
Showing you enough respect.

27
00:01:14,100 --> 00:01:14,900
Here.

28
00:01:15,981 --> 00:01:17,540
A hundred grand per handful.

29
00:01:17,701 --> 00:01:19,221
I'll pay whatever you stuff in.

30
00:01:21,141 --> 00:01:22,380
Such a great opportunity.

31
00:01:23,100 --> 00:01:24,180
Right, Peter?

32
00:01:26,180 --> 00:01:28,020
If someone pays me to do this,

33
00:01:28,981 --> 00:01:31,900
I'll stuff until they go bankrupt!

34
