legitimate pain♪

291
00:14:34,592 --> 00:14:38,464
♪You insist tears must rot on time♪

292
00:14:38,464 --> 00:14:42,976
♪Salvation's an infinite loop
of true or false♪

293
00:14:42,976 --> 00:14:51,040
♪The eraser rubs away what ought to be♪

294
00:15:15,668 --> 00:15:19,342
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

295
00:15:19,641 --> 00:15:22,832
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

296
00:15:24,664 --> 00:15:28,285
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

297
00:15:28,834 --> 00:15:31,633
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

298
00:15:33,104 --> 00:15:36,834
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

299
00:15:37,058 --> 00:15:40,640
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

300
00:15:41,954 --> 00:15:45,641
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

301
00:15:46,279 --> 00:15:51,394
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

302
00:15:52,098 --> 00:15:56,232
♪I feel guilty♪

303
00:15:56,802 --> 00:16:00,546
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

304
00:16:01,410 --> 00:16:04,853
♪Even in tears♪

305
00:16:05,602 --> 00:16:09,516
♪It doesn't matter♪

306
00:16:09,698 --> 00:16:13,521
♪We embrace in dreams♪

307
00:16:14,370 --> 00:16:17,808
♪I let down all my defenses♪

308
00:16:19,042 --> 00:16:22,405
♪Though the story has its end♪

309
00:16:23,170 --> 00:16:31,522
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
